<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Registration Complete • Scout Express</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/auth.css">
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <a href="/">Home</a>
  </header>

  <main>
    <div class="auth-wrapper">
      <div class="auth-container">
        <div class="success-message">
          <div class="success-icon">✓</div>
          <h2>Registration Complete!</h2>
          <p>Your profile has been successfully created. Our team will review your application and get back to you soon.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="auth-actions" style="justify-content: center;">
          <a class="btn-primary" href="/login" style="text-decoration: none; display: inline-block;">Go to Login</a>
        </div>

        <div class="create-account" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem;">
          <p><strong>What happens next?</strong></p>
          <ul style="text-align: left; display: inline-block; margin: 1rem 0;">
            <li>Your profile will be reviewed by our recruitment team</li>
            <li>You'll receive an email confirmation shortly</li>
            <li>If approved, you'll get access to job opportunities matching your profile</li>
            <li>You can update your profile anytime from your dashboard</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 ENSYNAPSE TECHNIQUE PRIVATE LIMITED. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>